highlights.text: “ไฟเย็น” by YOUNGOHM has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 963 days straight.
“ฉันรู้ดี” by Spoonfulz is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 60 spots at #138.
Saran has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “รออยู่อย่างนั้น” is the highest at #35.
“โปรดส่งเรามาคู่กันอีกได้ไหม” by โชเลย์ ชคัทพล is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #181.
